title: RHOC: Has-Beens & Wives
description:
The season 14 "Real Housewives of Orange County" reunion got off to a fiery, hilarious start this week, and we're here to rehash every minute: from Vicki's fuming that she's a has-been to Kelly calling Tamra a "dummy."

See acast.com/privacy for privacy and opt-out information.
